  <section xml:id="sec-random-variables">
    <title>Random variables</title>

    <introduction>
      <p>
        It's often useful to model a process using what's called a random variable. 
        Such a model allows us to apply a mathematical framework and statistical 
        principles for better understanding and predicting outcomes in the real world.
      </p>
    </introduction>

